{"type": "article", "id": 28469, "title": "灵感来源于雕塑的台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-21T06:46:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130451fjsmWUM26YQNiuCe.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>艺术雕塑缩小后制作成灯具会是什么样？以色列设计师 <a href=\"http://ronarad.archivestudio.co.uk/\">Ron Arad</a> 最近为 <a href=\"https://www.ingo-maurer.com/de/\">Ingo Maurer</a> 设计了一款名为 Spyre 的限量版灯具，它的设计灵感来源于 Arad 此前在 2016 英国皇家艺术学院（<a href=\"https://www.royalacademy.org.uk/\">Royal Academy of Arts</a>）夏季展览上展出的 16 米高的同名雕塑。灯具采用的是和原版雕塑相同的动力原件，由磁性相连的五个部分均可以自由进行移动和调节，造型非常多变。这款灯具限量 50 件，可以在学院的商店<a href=\"https://shop.royalacademy.org.uk/ron-arad-spyre-limited-edition-lamp.html\">购买</a>，售价 6000 英镑。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130449WmZPbjcGvzkYQxqp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130449pXQgUdY3JSRk5Hf1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130449W4Omi13puRcafM5N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130450AVtMS4WryjdQwcE8.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8007335\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}